                    <div class="CustomerReviewSummary">This Wonderul Book Is Helpful To All </div>
                    <div>
                      <span class="ItemCaption">Rating: </span>
                      <span>5</span>
                      <span class="ItemCaption">Helpful: </span>
                      <span>0</span>
                      /
                      <span>0</span>
                      votes <span class="ItemCaption">Reviewed: </span>
                      <span>2005-05-14</span>
                    </div>
                    <span>Panic To Power is a great starting place for those wanting to learn more about stress, anxiety, and more.  Stress leads to anxiety and stress can cause many health problems.  I know because I have been there and my stress turned into Anxiety Disorder, which led to Panic Disorder, severe Panic Attacks, Agoraphobia, Bi-Polar and more.
<br />
<br />This book offers tips on Positive Self-Talk, Self-Esteem, Nutrition, Assertivness, Medication suggestions and so much more.  It is so true to life that you will even laugh and really think hard at times.  I have ordered the Attacting Anxiety program from Midwest Centers which Lucinda started many years ago.  The actual workbook reads, "A Self-help, Self-Awareness Program for Stress, Anxiety, & Depression."
<br />
<br />In case you do not know know; Lucinda has a degree in nursing and her grade point average was 4.0.  Just watching the "Jump Start" tape/CD with her, Dr. Fisher, and others is a sign that there is hope.  I also enjoy listening to the CD lessons.  It is also available in cassette format.  They will work out a payment plan for you and you may request information to be sent to your doctor.  There is a possiblilty that your insurance may cover part of the cost however, you and your doctor may have to do some detective work on that part.  More information is in the "Panic To Power" book on how to do this.
<br />
<br />I highly suggest that you at least check it out.  I learned things by watching the "Jump Start" CD and reading this book that in ten years of treatment with various doctors they never ever told me.  Since I read the book and watched that CD, I am now more involved in my treatment.  When I went to my next therapist visit, I inquired as to why in 10 years not one single doctor or therapist offered this information, which would have kept me from ending up where I am today.  I urge you to order this book and read it.  If you read this book and like it, there is no doubt you will benefit from ordering the program.  Please do not wait, your life is waiting.
<br />
<br /></span>
                  
                    <div class="CustomerReviewSummary">Magnesium may speed up relief; please read this review!</div>
                    <div>
                      <span class="ItemCaption">Rating: </span>
                      <span>4</span>
                      <span class="ItemCaption">Helpful: </span>
                      <span>1</span>
